火灾报告中披露了迪迪涉嫌纵火袭击卡迪小子汽车的新细节https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-details-about-diddys-alleged-arson-attack-on-kid-cudis-car-revealed-in-fire-report-3797916?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=关于迪迪斯涉嫌纵火袭击儿童库迪斯汽车的新细节火灾报告Laura MolloySat, 28 Sep 2024 08:08:56 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3797916 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>此前，Cassie 去年 11 月提起的诉讼中披露了涉嫌纵火袭击的细节</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-details-about-diddys-alleged-arson-attack-on-kid-cudis-car-revealed-in-fire-report-3797916">火灾报告中披露的关于吹牛老爹涉嫌纵火袭击卡迪小子汽车的新细节</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/diddy-kid-cudi@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>洛杉矶市消防局最新出土的一份报告披露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diddy">“吹牛老爹”肖恩·库姆斯</a>涉嫌纵火袭击<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-cudi">卡迪小子</a>汽车的新信息。</p><p>第一个细节出现在去年 11 月，当时卡西（真名卡桑德拉·文图拉）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cassie-accuses-sean-diddy-combs-rape-abuse-lawsuit-3542013">提起诉讼，指控库姆斯强奸了她，并使她遭受了无数的性虐待、身体虐待、情感虐待和精神虐待</a>，其中一些据称包括她被迫库姆斯拍摄这些行为时与男妓发生性关系。</p><p>在他们的关系不稳定期间，卡西曾于 2012 年与说唱歌手 Kid Cudi（真名 Scott Mescudi）短暂约会，据报道这激怒了库姆斯。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-of-blowing-up-kid-cudis-car-3542030">根据诉讼，库姆斯威胁要炸毁卡迪小子的汽车，以便向他传达信息</a>。诉讼称：“大约在那时，卡迪小子的汽车在他的车道上爆炸。”</p><p> Kid Cudi 证实了这一说法，他通过发言人表示：“这都是真的。”</p><p>现在， <em><a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/kid-cudi-car-arson-fire-report-cassie-diddy-1235115198/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《滚石》杂志</a></em>获得的一份报告显示，Kid Cudi 是一辆保时捷的车主，这辆保时捷于 2012 年 1 月 9 日在洛杉矶的一个地址（通过公共记录与 Mescudi 连接）被“燃烧装置”点燃。火灾原因被列为“故意”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3794608" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794608" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794608" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Sean-Diddy-Combs.-CREDIT_-Shareif-Ziyadat_Getty-Images-for-Sean-_Diddy_-Combs.jpg" alt="肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯。图片来源：Shareif Ziyadat/Getty Images for Sean “Diddy” Combs" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Sean-Diddy-Combs.-CREDIT_-Shareif-Ziyadat_Getty-Images-for-Sean-_Diddy_-Combs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Sean-Diddy-Combs.-CREDIT_-Shareif-Ziyadat_Getty-Images-for-Sean-_Diddy_-Combs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Sean-Diddy-Combs.-CREDIT_-Shareif-Ziyadat_Getty-Images-for-Sean-_Diddy_-Combs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Sean-Diddy-Combs.-CREDIT_-Shareif-Ziyadat_Getty-Images-for-Sean-_Diddy_-Combs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Sean-Diddy-Combs.-CREDIT_-Shareif-Ziyadat_Getty-Images-for-Sean-_Diddy_-Combs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Sean-Diddy-Combs.-CREDIT_-Shareif-Ziyadat_Getty-Images-for-Sean-_Diddy_-Combs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794608" class="wp-caption-text">肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯。图片来源：Shareif Ziyadat/Getty Images for Sean “Diddy” Combs</figcaption></figure><p>文件显示，火灾首次报告时间为上午 10 点 53 分，造成估计价值 10,000 美元的损失。报告中没有提及嫌疑人。</p><p>检察官上周在反对保释迪迪的法庭文件中披露了涉嫌纵火的更多细节。在 9 月 17 日致法院的一封信中，他们声称，代表这位说唱歌手行事的同谋于 2012 年 1 月上旬“切开汽车的敞篷车顶并在车内扔进了燃烧弹”，从而纵火焚烧了一辆身份不明的车辆。据<em>《滚石》杂志</em>报道，“多名证人”将出庭作证，据称“吹嘘他在摧毁 individual-1 的汽车中所扮演的角色”。</p><p>吹牛老爹的律师马克·阿格尼菲洛 (Marc Agnifilo) 告诉该刊物：“没有任何指控表明库姆斯先生参与了这些行动或指示其他人采取这些行动。很明显，政府不知道是谁放火烧了这辆车，也不知道这与库姆斯先生有何关系，库姆斯先生否认与此事有任何关系。”</p><p>卡迪小子没有对这起袭击事件发表进一步评论。</p><p>这位说唱大亨上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-arrested-sexual-misconduct-allegations-3794341">在纽约被捕</a>，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-charged-with-sex-trafficking-racketeering-and-transporting-for-prostitution-3794598">指控犯有性贩运、敲诈勒索和运送卖淫罪</a>。如果罪名成立，他可能面临最低 15 年监禁和最高无期徒刑的强制性判决。库姆斯对针对他的指控表示无罪。</p><p>迪迪<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-denied-bail-in-sex-trafficking-racketeering-case-3794666">被拒绝保释</a>，据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/p-diddy-reportedly-placed-on-suicide-watch-while-awaiting-trial-for-sex-crimes-3795772">在等待审判期间被置于自杀监视之下</a>。阿格尼菲洛告诉<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/09/20/diddy-placed-routine-suicide-watch-metropolitan-detention-center/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TMZ</em></a> ，自杀监视指令是作为针对“新的、备受瞩目的囚犯”的例行措施而发布的。最新报道显示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paranoid-diddy-reportedly-not-eating-prison-fear-poisoned-3796772">，由于担心中毒，他在监狱里没有进食</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3796779" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3796779" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3796779" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SeanDiddyCombs-2023-Getty.jpg" alt="迪迪监狱" width="1392" height="884" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SeanDiddyCombs-2023-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SeanDiddyCombs-2023-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SeanDiddyCombs-2023-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SeanDiddyCombs-2023-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SeanDiddyCombs-2023-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3796779" class="wp-caption-text">肖恩·“吹牛老爹”库姆斯，摄于 2023 年。图片来源：杰马尔伯爵夫人/盖蒂图片社国会黑人核心小组基金会</figcaption></figure><p>从去年卡西的诉讼开始，针对库姆斯的指控和诉讼浪潮层出不穷。迪迪否认了这些说法，但在诉讼提起第二天，两人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-and-singer-cassie-settle-abuse-lawsuit-one-days-after-filing-3542698">以“双方满意”的方式解决了诉讼</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newly-published-surveillance-footage-reveals-diddy-attacking-cassie-3757408">库姆斯攻击卡西的视频后来于五月向公众公布</a>，迪迪<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-apologises-for-inexcusable-2016-video-allegedly-showing-him-attacking-ex-cassie-3757559">也为他当时的行为道歉</a>。</p><p>去年 11 月，文图拉最初提起诉讼一周后，又对吹牛老爹提出了两项​​新指控；一名妇女<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-drugging-sexually-assaulting-woman-revenge-porn-lawsuit-3548549">声称库姆斯对她下药并对她进行了性侵犯</a>，另一名<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/third-accuser-files-claims-of-sexual-assault-against-sean-diddy-combs-3548864">妇女则声称库姆斯和歌手兼作曲家亚伦·霍尔在 1990 年或 1991 年轮流强奸了原告和她的朋友</a>，并补充说迪迪在几天后变得暴力。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-hits-back-at-sexual-assault-allegations-enough-is-enough-3554746">吹牛老爹在网上否认了所有针对他的指控</a>，但霍尔尚未回应这些指控。</p><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-of-sexual-harassment-and-assault-by-music-producer-3593467">制片人罗德尼·“利尔·罗德”·琼斯起诉库姆斯，指控他性侵犯他</a>，举办有性工作者和未成年女孩在场的派对，并强迫他与妓女上床。迪迪回复说，琼斯的说法“纯属虚构”。</p><p> 5 月 22 日，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-accused-of-drugging-and-sexually-assaulting-former-model-3758415">被指控对前模特克里斯托·麦金尼 (Crystal McKinney) 下药并进行殴打</a>。麦金尼指控他在 2003 年的一场男士时装周活动上对她进行了性侵犯，先给了她一个“强力”的关节，然后在浴室里对她进行了性侵犯。迪迪没有回应置评。</p><p> 7 月 4 日，一名前色情女演员也站出来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-porn-actress-accuses-diddy-of-sex-trafficking-3772132">指控这位说唱歌手进行性交易。</a>吹牛老爹的律师否认了这些说法，坚称“库姆斯先生从未对任何人进行过性侵犯或性贩运”。</p><p>本周早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-accused-of-raping-woman-on-video-in-latest-lawsuit-3796813">另一名女子出面指控迪迪和他的保镖在2001年对她下药、强奸并拍摄了这一事件</a>。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/sean-diddy-combs-sued-for-sexual-assault-distribution-of-video-1236154882/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Variety</a></em>报道，最新的受害者塔莉亚·格雷夫斯 (Thalia Graves) 在 9 月 24 日向纽约法院提起的诉讼中声称，库姆斯和他的同事约瑟夫·谢尔曼 (Joseph Sherman) 对她下药、性侵犯，并在未经同意的情况下拍摄了整个过程。</p><p>迪迪继续否认有任何不当行为。</p><p><strong>如需有关英国性骚扰、侵犯和强奸的帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> 。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-details-about-diddys-alleged-arson-attack-on-kid-cudis-car-revealed-in-fire-report-3797916">火灾报告中披露的有关迪迪涉嫌纵火袭击卡迪小子汽车的新细节</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
比约克预告了新的以气候为中心的“聚宝盆”音乐会电影https://www.nme.com/news/music/bjork-teases-new-climate-focused-cornucopia-concert-film-3797915?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bjork-teases-new-climate-focused-cornucopia-音乐会电影Hollie GeraghtySat, 28 Sep 2024 07:51:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternative https://www.nme.com/?p=3797915 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比约克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这部新电影捕捉了冰岛音乐偶像热情的气候行动主义</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bjork-teases-new-climate-focused-cornucopia-concert-film-3797915">比约克 (Björk) 预告了新的以气候为主题的“聚宝盆”音乐会影片，该影片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比约克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/bjork-cornucopia-concert-film-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-