e Richer</a> 1997 年开创性热门单曲《Kiss Me》的短视频，并附有一首更具舞曲流行风格的伴奏曲目。在歌曲上。</p><p>此后，粉丝们将这与卡彭特联系起来，认为丽莎在视频中穿的粉色服装符合这位“Espresso”歌手最近巡演服装的审美。</p><p>昨晚（9 月 26 日）卡彭特在密歇根州底特律的一场音乐会上翻唱了这首歌曲，进一步煽动了两人可能合作的谣言。此前有消息称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carptenter-scraps-custom-nonsense-outros-but-promises-surprise-cover-each-night-starting-with-abba-as-she-kicks-off-world-tour-3796700">她放弃了粉丝最喜欢的“Nonsense”尾声，转而</a>在她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-2024-north-american-the-short-n-sweet-tour-3767338">“Short N&#39; Sweet”巡回演唱会</a>中每晚表演新的翻唱。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@lalalalisa_m/video/7418734706700668191" data-video-id="7418734706700668191" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@lalalalisa_m" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@lalalalisa_m?refer=embed">@lalalalisa_m</a> </p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f319.png" alt="🌙" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f48b.png" alt="💋" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - 丽莎" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7418734709902445343?refer=embed">♬ 原声 – 丽莎</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 翻唱底特律 Sixpence None The Richer 的《Kiss Me》！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f399.png" alt="🎙" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DetroitShortnSweet?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DetroitShortnSweet</a><br /> <a href="https://t.co/sbf8E4w7gY">