f="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duff-mckagan">达夫·麦卡根 (Duff McKagan)</a>在下周开始的“灯塔”巡演之前分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie)</a>的《英雄》翻唱作品。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/guns-n-roses-live-at-glastonbury-photos-setlist-3460919">枪与玫瑰乐队在格拉斯顿伯里现场表演：一场精彩的表演......给了错误的观众</a></strong></li></ul><p>继去年年底发行个人专辑《Lighthouse》后，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">枪炮玫瑰</a>乐队的贝斯手正在欧洲、英国和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-duff-mckagan-announces-solo-us-tour-shares-new-concert-video-3761518">美国</a>进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-duff-mckagan-announces-2024-uk-and-european-solo-tour-buy-tickets-3618102">一系列演出</a>。巡演将于周一（9 月 30 日）在都柏林拉开帷幕，并将于 10 月在伦敦、华沙、柏林、米兰、巴黎等地停留，然后于下个月前往美国。</p><p>在登上舞台之前，麦卡根发布了鲍伊 1977 年热门单曲的翻唱版。 “我们认为在灯塔巡演前夕在这里推出几首新鲜歌曲是个好主意，”他在 Instagram 上写道。 “选择大卫·鲍伊的英雄对我来说似乎是一个自然的主题（当然，我是一个巨大的历史书呆子）......70 年代中期冷战时期柏林墙阴影下的不幸恋人。”</p><p>除了《英雄》之外，麦卡根还分享了一首新歌《True To The Death Rock N Roll Ballad》，他说自己写这首歌是为了“尝试和赞美”《英雄》所描绘的时代。这首华丽摇滚歌曲探讨了爱、欲望和时间的主题。查看下面的两条曲目。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Duff McKagan - 英雄 - 官方展示台" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Ps6q3uw-OU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="至死不渝摇滚民谣" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ulnw2D3JyY4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Lighthouse》是麦卡根作为独唱艺术家的第三张专辑，继 1993 年的首张专辑《Believe In Me》和 2019 年的《Tenderness》之后。客串演出的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-in-chains">Alice In Chains</a>吉他手 Jerry Cantrell 和枪炮与玫瑰乐队的长期乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a> 。</p><p>您可以在下面查看完整的巡演日期列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fduff-mckagan-tickets%2Fartist%2F5214854" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找英国和欧洲日期的门票，以及<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/duff-mckagan-tickets/artist/1311767?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=RgHWNZyYUxyKTIqQnV04UVzBUkCyYiRxgw1XSc0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2